snippet.title: NHL All-Star Hockey - Video Game Trailer. (1995) Sega Saturn.
snippet.description:
Official Trailer for video game NHL All-Star Hockey

Game developed by Gray Matter.
Published by Sega in 1995 for Sega Saturn.
A 2D rendered version was released the same year for Genesis/megadrive and another was released for Game Gear.

Video Found on the Sega Saturn Bootleg  CD Sampler.
